                    <span>At least the diversity of sports used in this tape kept my attention and I did like some of the stories. I even learned some things that I didn't know about some sports luminaries. I wouldn't buy the tape again. Come on, Jack, get some humor in your stories and on the tape. Not everything has to be so serious.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">great book on the good things in sports and life</div>
